  "subject": "workaround to insert groupentity tuple",
  "commit_message": "workaround to insert groupentity tuple\n\nThis is a workaround for the issue described in POLICY-486.\nThe benefit of this workaround is that it does not require to\nbuild new images, so it does not require a new load.\n\nIt takes advantage of the *tweaks.sh scripts, part of the \"docker-compose\"\nproject that is cloned for configuration previous to bring up the containers.\n\nChange-Id: I91c7b2682bade0f3c244e37f960dd841c21a2e64\nIssue-ID: POLICY-486\nSigned-off-by: Jorge Hernandez <jh1730@att.com>\n",
